PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777039866
OL,3,CPolice search for nine men involved in
OL,4,Cgang rape after ringleader jailed
OL,6,FWest Yorkshire Police said the other
OL,7,Fmen involved have not been identified.
OL,9,FA spokesperson said detectives would
OL,10,F"welcome any new information" to trace
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FLeeds Crown Court heard the woman met
OL,14,FWyatt after being told he could sell
OL,15,Fher cannabis.
OL,17,FWhen she went to his home, he refused
OL,18,Fto let her leave and raped her
OL,19,Fmultiple times, giving her drugs as
OL,20,Fshe cried.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
