OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777039866
OL,3,CPolice search for nine men involved in
OL,4,Cgang rape after ringleader jailed
OL,6,FNick Adlington, prosecuting, said:
OL,7,F"She described crying when he did it
OL,8,Fand him giving her a pipe of crack
OL,9,Fcocaine to stop her crying."
OL,11,FWyatt also gave the woman's partner
OL,12,Fcrack cocaine when he went to the
OL,13,Fproperty to ask after her.
OL,15,FAfter the other men arrived, the
OL,16,Fvictim was forced to remove her
OL,17,Funderwear.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
