PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777039866
OL,3,CPolice search for nine men involved in
OL,4,Cgang rape after ringleader jailed
OL,6,FMr Adlington said: "She made it clear
OL,7,Fshe did not want to have sex and
OL,8,Fcried. She stated it went on until
OL,9,F5am."
OL,11,FShe was taunted and called names
OL,12,Fduring the incident, before some of
OL,13,Fthe men threw cash at her.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the victim spoke of
OL,16,Frecurring nightmares following the
OL,17,Fattack.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
