FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777039866
OL,3,CPolice search for nine men involved in
OL,4,Cgang rape after ringleader jailed
OL,6,F"It has had the biggest impact on my
OL,7,Frelationship and it has been really
OL,8,Fhard to talk about it with my partner
OL,9,Fand he finds it really hard to talk
OL,10,Fabout," she said.
OL,12,F"I lost control of my bladder when I'm
OL,13,Fscared. My sleep has been affected as
OL,14,FI have nightmares about being raped.
OL,15,FIt is like I am reliving it."
OL,17,FWyatt, a former painter and decorator,
OL,18,Fwas convicted last month of two counts
OL,19,Fof rape and other sex offences.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
