SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777039866
OL,3,CPolice search for nine men involved in
OL,4,Cgang rape after ringleader jailed
OL,6,FGiles Grant, for Wyatt, said his
OL,7,Fclient was a father who had raised his
OL,8,Ffamily "departed from a lifestyle of
OL,9,Fdrugs". He told the court Wyatt had
OL,10,Flost one son last year, but continued
OL,11,Fto have a relationship with his other
OL,12,Fson.
OL,14,FJailing Wyatt, Judge Ray Singh said
OL,15,Fthe attack "humiliated and degraded"
OL,16,Fthe womanvand would have an "immense"
OL,17,Fand lasting impact.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
