OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777039866
OL,3,CPolice search for nine men involved in
OL,4,Cgang rape after ringleader jailed
OL,6,F"The final act of humiliation was when
OL,7,Fthey threw money at her and you
OL,8,Fcollected it and congratulated her on
OL,9,Fhaving made some good money," he said.
OL,11,FFollowing the sentencing, Det Ch Insp
OL,12,FLisa Jones, of the West Yorkshire
OL,13,FPolice Modern Slavery and Human
OL,14,FTrafficking Team, said: "Wyatt preyed
OL,15,Fon the victim, who was clearly very
OL,16,Fvulnerable, and cruelly exploited her
OL,17,Fin the most appalling of
OL,18,Fcircumstances, raping her on several
OL,19,Foccasions and forcing her into being
OL,20,Fraped by multiple other men at the
OL,21,Fsame time."
OL,26,@vD@YOU
