OL,3,CPolice search for nine men involved in
OL,4,Cgang rape after ringleader jailed
OL,6,FShe added: "The lasting traumatic
OL,7,Fimpact that Wyatt's actions have had
OL,8,Fon her cannot be underestimated, and
OL,9,Fwe hope it will provide some degree of
OL,10,Fcomfort to her to see him brought to
OL,11,Fjustice."
